    {\displaystyle \lim _{N\to \infty }{1 \over N}\sum _{n=0}^{N-1}\left|\int _{X}f\circ T^{n}\cdot gd\mu -\int _{X}f\,d\mu \cdot \int _{X}g\,d\mu \right|=0.}
  A dynamical system 
  
    
      
        (
        X
        ,
        
          
            A
          
        
        ,
        μ
        ,
        T
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle (X,{\mathcal {A}},\mu ,T)}
